01:00:46.120 --> 01:00:55.550 align:middle line:84%
And since x sub
n converges to 0,

01:00:55.550 --> 01:00:58.690 align:middle line:84%
there exists
natural number n sub

01:00:58.690 --> 01:01:06.120 align:middle line:84%
0 such that if n is bigger
than or equal to M0,

01:01:06.120 --> 01:01:15.430 align:middle line:84%
then x sub n minus the
limit, which is just 0,

01:01:15.430 --> 01:01:17.470 align:middle line:84%
