which is just x sub n.

01:02:12.610 --> 01:02:15.490 align:middle line:84%
Now, it's also-- so we didn't
strictly speaking prove this--

01:02:15.490 --> 01:02:25.660 align:middle line:84%
but it's not too hard to show
that square roots respect

01:02:25.660 --> 01:02:26.750 align:middle line:90%
