01:02:33.910 --> 01:02:43.570 align:middle line:90%


01:02:43.570 --> 01:02:50.055 align:middle line:84%
So the second case
is x not equal to 0.

01:02:50.055 --> 01:02:52.630 align:middle line:90%


01:02:52.630 --> 01:02:58.280 align:middle line:84%
And to do this case, we'll
use those two theorems again.

01:02:58.280 --> 01:03:02.360 align:middle line:90%


01:03:02.360 --> 01:03:07.970 align:middle line:84%
And let's look at square root of
